name: mal kasablanka, jakarta. circa 2014.
description:
jakarta is also known as a big malls, in every direction there's always a mall. from the high class to the low class. like this one i captured. it was a mall in south jakarta that always full at weekend and can cause a 15km traffic jammed because the cars waiting to in or just drop and pick up its passengers.
